code: @Override protected boolean lessThan(InternalGeoGridBucket o1, InternalGeoGridBucket o2) {     int cmp = Long.compare(o2.getDocCount(), o1.getDocCount()).     if (cmp == 0) {         cmp = o2.compareTo(o1).         if (cmp == 0) {             cmp = System.identityHashCode(o2) - System.identityHashCode(o1).         }     }     return cmp > 0. }
